event.title: Ambyar Concert Yogyakarta 2023
event.description: Take advantage of the Ambyar Concert Yogyakarta 2023 featuring today's popular music and an exceptional performance by Denny Caknan, Guyon Waton, Gilga Sahid, NDX A.K.A, Happy Asmara, Yenni Inka, Aftershine and more. It's on October 1 - 4, 2023, at Prambanan Temple, Yogyakarta, Indonesia. Make sure to secure your tickets before they sell out. This is an event you will want to attend!
event.highlight: Watch Ambyar Concert Yogyakarta 2023 featuring Denny Caknan, Guyon Waton, Gilga Sahid, NDX A.K.A, Happy Asmara, Yenni Inka, Aftershine and more!, The concert will be held on October 1 - 4, 2023, at Prambanan Temple, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.
